    Data example of logistic provider selection problem.

    example_cocoso.Rd

    Information of decision-making matrix from a logistic provider selection problem including information about criteria, alternatives and weights.

    example_cocoso

    Format

    A data frame with 10 rows and 6 columns.

    Source

    Extract in "A combined compromise solution (CoCoSo) method for multi-criteria decision-making problems", Yazdani, M., Zarate, P., Kazimieras Zavadskas, E., & Turskis, Z. (2019), https://doi.org/10.1108/MD-05-2017-0458.

    example_cocoso
